{'id': 14967619, 'body': 'Hello,   

At bunq we always strive to be the bank that perfectly fits our users wants and needs. That’s why we asked them what we could do to help them increase their green impact. 81% of them voted for planting more trees.   

For this reason, we decided to simplify our subscription plans (that reached more than 10 offers) to make it easier for our users to choose the subscription that suits them. 👍', 'modified': '2020-04-28T12:57:49Z'}

{'id': 13661801, 'body': "Hey, 

Thank you for your feedback. We'll take it into account to improve our App. 

At bunq, we always try to provide support in the language of our users if possible but since we are a European bank before being a Dutch one, it is not always possible. However, we made sure to integrate automated translations in our support chat to make our users experience easier. Concerning the activation of your card, you'll see thatyou can only do it with the Pincode you previously chose which means your money is completely safe 🙂👍", 'modified': '2020-02-24T08:58:58Z'}

{'id': 13623100, 'body': 'Hello, 

We do indeed provide support through text only since it makes it easier for both sides to keep track of what has been said more easily and to avoid that our users have to wait on hold why we fix their issues. However our support team is available every day of the year on the same chat and via the same email address which is Support@bunq.com. 

If you were charged because you used the switch service, you should know that this amount  is charged to cover the amount we need to pay to this service. 👍🏻', 'modified': '2020-02-21T09:49:40Z'}

{'id': 13622566, 'body': 'Hi Marco,

Thanks for your feeback! We always take it into account to improve our app. It seems that the payments you refer to may have taken a moment to be updated in the app. If you have any doubt, you can always export a bank statement like this:https://together.bunq.com/d/3207 👍
', 'modified': '2020-02-21T09:32:22Z'}

