You can discuss it further with our support team via support@bunq.com 👍", 'modified': '2020-05-20T10:56:32Z'}

{'id': 3464348, 'body': 'Hi Johan,

This is definitely not the service we strive to provide our users. Could let us know via the support chat or support@bunq.com, what exactly is that you are struggling with? We would love to receive your feedback and assist with anything that is necessary. 

Regards', 'modified': '2018-05-14T20:33:02Z'}

{'id': 3386553, 'body': "Hi! 

I'm sorry you feel this way. You can always revert to free if you don't wish to enjoy the full Premium features. You can do so by following the next: Tap on your profile picture (top right corner)> Tap on My Subscriptions > revert to Free. 
In any case, you can always reach us at any time on the private chat with our Support team. Tap on Together (bottom right corner)> Tap on Private Matters and we'll help you right away! 👍", 'modified': '2018-05-07T20:15:19Z'}

{'id': 3131121, 'body': "We're happy to see you happy. 🙂👍

